Name: CornerMP-aqua
Summary: a featured skin for MPlayer

Author: DC.Park <pdc@kaist.ac.kr>
URL: http://www.MPlayerHQ.hu/homepage/dload.html

%description
CornerMP-aqua resides in the bottom-right of your desktop corner.
It does not disturb you in your watching the movies. :)


%prep
# Untar CornerMP-aqua.tar.bz2 with -xfj options.
# ( eg.  $ tar xfj CornerMP-aqua.tar.bz2 )

%install
# Move CornerMP-aqua to your MPlayer Skin directory.
# ( eg.  $ mv CornerMP-aqua /usr/local/share/mplayer/Skin/ )

%clean
# Delete the CornerMP-aqua.tar.bz2 if unnecessary. :)
# ( eg. $ rm CornerMP-aqua.tar.bz2 )


